 monetize and offer deals discounts and coupons to a database of users that are on property or at the event in real time the company was formerly known as sound kitchen entertainment group inc and changed its name to first level entertainment group inc in august  first level first level entertainment group inc operates in the entertainment business in the united states the company focuses on developing mobile applications its products include vipwink a mobile application that enables individuals brands and others with a twitter following to differentiate and monetize their fans and followers and mobilesonars a white label mobile application which allows a partner site to monetize and offer deals discounts and coupons to a database of users that are on property or at the event in real time the company was formerly known as sound kitchen entertainment group inc and changed its name to first level entertainment group inc in august  first level entertainment group inc was founded in  and is based in fort lauderdale florida detailed description  south andrews avenuesuite fort lauderdale fl united statesfounded in  phone  wwwfleginccom key executives for first level entertainment group inc mr steven adelstein chairman and chief executive officer age  mr robert f hussey president and director age  mr alfred j fernandez chief financial officer principal accounting officer secretary and director age  mr steven mark berman chief operating officer and director age  compensation as of fiscal year  first level entertainment group inc key developments first level entertainment group inc announced delayed q filing jan   on  first level entertainment group inc announced that they will be unable to file their next q by the deadline required by the sec first level entertainment group inc announced delayed annual k filing nov   on  first level entertainment group inc announced that they will be unable to file their next k by the deadline required by the sec first level entertainment g