asting system acquired castle rock entertainment on december   and even new line cinema on january   on october   time warner acquired turner broadcasting system thus bringing the pre silentsound film and preaugust  cartoon libraries back home however castle rock entertainments pre library is currently owned by metrogoldwynmayer and as such warner bros owns castle rock entertainments post library on october   warner bros added the peanuts library to its under license from peanuts worldwide llc licensor and owner of the peanuts material this includes all of the television library outside of the theatrical library which continues to be a joint venture between cbs corporation and paramount pictures both companies part of national amusements in  warner bros shut down new line cinema as an independent minimajor studio so they added the new line cinema film and television collections to their library the next year on october   warner bros acquired home video distribution rights to the sesame street library in conjunction with sesame workshop in june  it created the harry potter global franchise development team hpgfdt group to oversee it ownership of the harry potter franchise worldwide including trademark to wizarding world highestgrossing films domestically highestgrossing films rank title year domestic gross notes  the dark knight    the dark knight rises    harry potter and the deathly hallows part     american sniper    batman v superman dawn of justice    suicide squad    harry potter and the philosophers stone    the hobbit an unexpected journey   coowned by new line cinema and metrogoldwynmayer pictures the films producers  harry potter and the halfblood prince    harry potter and the deathly hallows part     inception    harry potter and the order of the phoenix    man of steel    harry potter and the goblet of fire    the matrix reloaded    the hangover    gravity    harry potter and the chamber of secrets    the hobbit the desolation of smaug   coowned by new l