e released through may  but only following bluray and dvd releases in  warner bros set studio and industry records raking in  billion in domestic receipts and  billion worldwide warner bros harry potter film series was the worldwide highestgrossing film series of all time without adjusting for inflation its batman film series was one of only two series to have two entries earn more than  billion worldwide harry potter and the deathly hallows – part  was warner bros highestgrossing movie ever surpassing the dark knight however the harry potter movies have produced a net loss due to hollywood accounting imax corp signed with warner bros pictures in april  to release as many as  giantformat films through  warner bros formed a short form digital unit blue ribbon content under its warner bros animation  warner digital series president on february   columbia tristar warner filmes de portugal ltda a joint venture with sony pictures which distributed both companies films in portugal announced that it would have its offices no more from march   nos audiovisuais is handling the distribution of warner bros films in portugal since then as of  warner bros is one of only three studios to have released a pair of billiondollar films in the same year along with walt disney studios motion pictures and universal studios the distinction was achieved in  with the dark knight rises and the hobbit an unexpected journey as of  it is only studio to cross  billion at the domestic boxoffice every year since  on november   time warner through warner bros announced that it had bought machinima inc making it a subsidiary of warner bros digital networks production deals active producerdistributor deals as of march  alcon entertainment – langley park productions – lin pictures – malpaso productions pearl street films –  ratpacdune entertainment – springhill entertainment – syncopy inc – team downey – vertigo entertainment formerly rl films – village roadshow pictures – former producer deals appian