oproduction with legendary entertainment and toho the lego movie –present coproduction with village roadshow pictures and warner animation group fantastic beasts and where to find them –present film series projected to run until  acquired libraries mergers and acquisitions have helped warner bros accumulate a diverse collection of films cartoons and television programs in the aftermath of the  antitrust suit uncertain times led warner bros in  to sell most of its pre films and cartoons to the nowdefunct holding company associated artists productions aap in addition aap also obtained the fleischer studios and famous studios popeye cartoons originally from paramount pictures two years later aap was sold to united artists which held them until  when metrogoldwynmayer acquired united artists in  during their independent years turner broadcasting system acquired brut productions the film production arm of francebased thenstruggling personalcare company faberge inc in  turner broadcasting system by then having failed to acquire metrogoldwynmayer settled for ownership of the metrogoldwynmayerunited artists library this included almost all of the premay  mgm film and television libraries with the exception of the films  television series owned by united artists ie james bond franchise although some united artists material were included such as the aap library north american rights to a majority of the rko radio pictures library and the television series gilligans islandcitation needed in  warner communications acquired the library of film and television company lorimar this acquisition included the post library of rankinbass productions as well as the post library of monogram picturesallied artists pictures corporation which the lorimar library included in  turner broadcasting system acquired animation studio hannabarbera and rubyspears from taft broadcasting and years later turner broadcasting system acquired castle rock entertainment on december   and even new line cinema on january   on october   time warner acquired turner broadcasting system thus bringing the pre silentsound film and preaugust  cartoon libraries back home however castle rock entertainments pre library is currently owned by metrogoldwynmayer and as such warner bros owns castle rock entertainments post library on october   warner bros added the peanuts library to its under license from peanuts worldwide llc licensor and owner of the peanuts material this includes all of the television library outside of the theatrical library which continues to be a joint venture between cbs corporation and paramount pictures both companies part of national amusements in  warner bros shut down new line cinema as an independent minimajor studio so they added the new line cinema film and television collections to their library the next year on october   warner bros acquired home video distribution rights to the sesame street library in conjunction with sesame workshop in june  it created the harry potter global franchise development team hpgfdt group to oversee it ownership of the harry potter franchise worldwide including trademark to wizarding world highestgrossing films domestically highestgrossing films rank title year domestic gross notes  the dark knight    the dark knight rises    harry potter and the deathly hallows part     american sniper    batman v superman dawn of justice    suicide squad    harry potter and the philosophers stone    the hobbit an unexpected journey   coowned by new line cinema and metrogoldwynmayer pictures the films producers  harry potter and the halfblood prince    harry potter and the deathly hallows part     inception    harry potter and the order of the phoenix    man of steel    harry potter and the goblet of fire    the matrix reloaded    the hangover    gravity    harry potter and the chamber of secrets    the hobbit the desolation of smaug   coowned by new line cinema and metrogoldwynmayer pictures the films producers  the lego movie    i am l